103
00:04:42,790 --> 00:04:47,130
♪Matahari senja mendengar bisikanmu♪

104
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:52,290
♪Terlalu banyak rahasia
Kuceritakan padamu♪

105
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:55,270
♪Terlalu manis♪

106
